        select distinct sessionId,orderId,timestamp,row_number() over (partition by orderId order by timestamp asc) as rn 
        from `last14Days(orderSuccessView)`
    ) where rn=1
),

b as(
    select a.sessionId,ao.createdDate,ao.orderId,ao.guid 
    from `temp.attributed_Orders` ao left join a on a.orderId=ao.orderId 
    where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),ao.orderDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 14
),

c as( 
    select distinct * from (
        select orderId,to_date(from_unixTime(createdDate/1000)) as ot,guid,to_date(from_unixTime(endTime /1000)) as vt ,row_number() over (partition by orderId order by endTime desc) as rn 
        from b left join `last14Days(sessionSummary)` ss on ss.lastGuid=b.guid and ss.endTime<createdDate 
        order by orderId desc
    ) where rn=1
)

select ot, case when datediff(ot,vt)=0 then 0 when datediff(ot,vt)=1 then 1  when datediff(ot,vt)<=5 then 2 when datediff(ot,vt)<=10 then 3 else 4 end as visit,
count(distinct orderId) as orders, count(distinct orderId) * 100.0 / (select count(*) from c where ot='2023-02-03') as percentage 
from c where ot='2023-02-03' 
group by ot, case when datediff(ot,vt)=0 then 0 when datediff(ot,vt)=1 then 1  when datediff(ot,vt)<=5 then 2 when datediff(ot,vt)<=10 then 3 else 4 end order by visit

",1000)
